\section*{Goal}

We study whether citronellal odor puff stimulation changes the firing
rate of cockroach antennal lobe neurons. Specifically, we compare the
response of three neurons and determine whether the stimulus effect is
consistent across neurons.

The analysis follows four steps:

\begin{enumerate}
\item Visualize spike trains with raster plots
\item Form qualitative hypotheses
\item Fit a non-homogeneous Poisson process (NHPP) model
\item Evaluate stimulus effects for each neuron
\end{enumerate}

%------------------------------------------------
